acceptance_criteria: "list/search/context accept --format ndjson emitting exactly one self-contained JSON object per line (no wrapper, no trailing summary on stdout); works with head/grep/jq -c round-trips and stays EPIPE-clean; field names identical to --json mode; contracts/MCP/completions/docs/completions regenerated; covered by unit + pipeline-style tests"
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
